snippet.textDisplay:
Beyond the words can describe... What a goose-bumpy number! Perfect melody building mood towards an upbeat rhythm... और मोहे भी "लागी, लागी, लागी, लागी, लागी, लागी, लागी, लागी, लागी रे लगन चितचोर..." Shantanuji and Swanandji have been a great combination creating heartfelt and moving compositions all the time and this one is no different either. 


And Kaushiki Chakroborty... Waah! Kya Kehna. Absolutely enchanting beat!
